the scales of the temperature contours differ by three orders of magnitude. The\nspatial resolution can be as high as 20 nanometers thanks to the continuous\nnature of the thin film.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Nov 2020 21:17:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-23"}
